<a name="0">[0]</a> <a href="#0" id=0>Information loses through transformation from the internal representation to the form of display.</a>
<a name="1">[1]</a> <a href="#1" id=1>The original structure of the core representations takes the priority to appear in summary.</a>
<a name="2">[2]</a> <a href="#2" id=2>A summarization can be satisfied only when it matches the personal space of the reader.</a>
<a name="3">[3]</a> <a href="#3" id=3>3D printer extends display from cyberspace to the physical space.</a>
<a name="4">[4]</a> <a href="#4" id=4>Inventing a new interface that can easily convey representations through multiple channels is a way to improve human understanding.</a>
<a name="5">[5]</a> <a href="#5" id=5>The personal spaces reflect personal reading experience, interests and knowledge based on the texts that have been read.</a>
<a name="6">[6]</a> <a href="#6" id=6>Optimizing the layout of display needs to consider three dimensions.</a>
<a name="7">[7]</a> <a href="#7" id=7>The reason is that authors are the best person to organize his representation.</a>
<a name="8">[8]</a> <a href="#8" id=8>New interface devices like 3D monitor will significantly influence the representation of summary.</a>
<a name="9">[9]</a> <a href="#9" id=9>Humans experience in a multi-dimensional space but have to use a two-dimensional media such as paper and screen to externalize representation.</a>
<a name="10">[10]</a> <a href="#10" id=10>Previous research on text summarization neglects the innovation of displaying summary as researchers assume that the form of output is the same as the input.</a>
<a name="11">[11]</a> <a href="#11" id=11>Summarization carries out in an interaction environment where people read, write, cite and communicate with personal spaces.</a>
<a name="12">[12]</a> <a href="#12" id=12>To reflect not only reading characteristics but also understanding characteristics, it is a reasonable method to combine the linear organization with the order of generalization and specialization.</a>
<a name="13">[13]</a> <a href="#13" id=13>Structuring summary in an appropriate form is important as summary is mainly for human to read and understand.</a>
